title: USA Red Light & Speed Cameras | POI 2015
description:
All USA speed and red light camera locations, biggest DB currently available . 
POI file for all popular GPS brands.
CSV files, make sure you know how to install them.
*****
 
Speed camera GPS locations in the USA. This USA POI GPS file will help you to detect high risk locations and to adjust your speed. Here you can download GPS POI file with all speed camera locations in the USA, a part of a GPS POI data collection with over 5000 speed camera and red light camera locations in North America (combined).Our POI files can be used onto Garmin, Magellan, CoPilot, Destinator, Streets & Trips and many other more or less popular GPS SatNav brands
